{"results":[{"aya":"029","id":4704,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他的女人便喊叫著走来，她打自己的脸，说：我是一个不能生育的老妇人。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"030","id":4705,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他们说：你的主是这样说的，他确是至睿的，确是全知的。 　","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"031","id":4706,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他说：诸位使者啊！你们有什么差事呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"032","id":4707,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他们说：我们确已奉派去惩治一群犯罪的民众，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"033","id":4708,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"我们将因毁灭他们而降下黏土变成的石头，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"034","id":4709,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"那是从你的主那里为过分者而发出的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"035","id":4710,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"我把城里所有的信士都救了出来，","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":9,"previousPage":"/zh/s051-4.json","nextPage":"/zh/s051-6.json"}}